title: Pruning Plant By Plant
description:
Pruning Plant By Plant by DK Publishing


Overview: With clear text and illustrations that explain the reasons for pruning and exactly where and how to cut, Pruning Plant by Plant is a handy visual guide that covers all the most popular plants. Whether its fruit trees, soft fruits, or vines, Pruning Plant by Plant includes advice on pruning 170 of the most widely-grown shrubs and climbers, with easy-to-follow instructions for gardeners of all levels. Pruning Plant by Plant's small, fits-in-the-pocket format is perfect for carrying around while gardening
